    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.6728798707
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、すまない。客席を見ていたんだ\n今日のチケットは完売で、会場は満員だと聞いてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ああ、すまない。客席を見ていたんだ\n今日のチケットは完売で、会場は満員だと聞いてね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.6728798707,
      "endTime": 15.630838855199999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.8308389505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "今日だけじゃありませんよ\nどの街でも、会場は満員御礼だったじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "今日だけじゃありませんよ\nどの街でも、会場は満員御礼だったじゃないですか",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.8308389505,
      "endTime": 22.4335375627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.6335374673
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……星見プロのアイドルで全国ツアーをして\n日本中の会場をお客さんで一杯にする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そうだな……星見プロのアイドルで全国ツアーをして\n日本中の会場をお客さんで一杯にする……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6335374673,
      "endTime": 30.1991610369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなのおかげで、入社した頃からの夢が叶ったよ\nありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "みんなのおかげで、入社した頃からの夢が叶ったよ\nありがとう",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4124943893,
      "endTime": 35.844034687699995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.0449196339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "お礼を言うのはまだ早いですよ\n最後のライブも成功させて、有終の美を飾りましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "お礼を言うのはまだ早いですよ\n最後のライブも成功させて、有終の美を飾りましょう！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0449196339,
      "endTime": 43.2698177816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "愛もしっかりしてきたな\n今日はいつも以上に頼もしく感じるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "愛もしっかりしてきたな\n今日はいつも以上に頼もしく感じるよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.4764844101,
      "endTime": 48.8206566971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.0339899541
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか？　もしそう見えるとしたら\n今回のツアーで、いい影響を受けたのかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そうですか？　もしそう見えるとしたら\n今回のツアーで、いい影響を受けたのかもしれません",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.0339899541,
      "endTime": 57.4901350499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "ツアー中、いろんなメンバーと交流して\nみなさんと密度の濃い時間を過ごしてきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ツアー中、いろんなメンバーと交流して\nみなさんと密度の濃い時間を過ごしてきました",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6768016022,
      "endTime": 64.26847955400001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.4751461825
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "それで改めて思ったんです\n星見プロのアイドルは、全員が主役なんだって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "それで改めて思ったんです\n星見プロのアイドルは、全員が主役なんだって……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.4751461825,
      "endTime": 71.7751461825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "一人一人違う魅力があって、知れば知るほど\n新しい発見があって、ますます好きになって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "一人一人違う魅力があって、知れば知るほど\n新しい発見があって、ますます好きになって……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9751460871,
      "endTime": 79.7250781855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.9117447378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "そんな魅力的な人達から、ツアーをきっかけに沢山の\n刺激をもらって、私自身もひと皮剥けた気がするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そんな魅力的な人達から、ツアーをきっかけに沢山の\n刺激をもらって、私自身もひと皮剥けた気がするんです",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9117447378,
      "endTime": 88.47052044889999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.6771869821
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "刺激を受けたのは愛だけじゃないぞ\nみんなも愛からいい刺激をもらったと思っているさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "刺激を受けたのは愛だけじゃないぞ\nみんなも愛からいい刺激をもらったと思っているさ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6771869821,
      "endTime": 94.8399761363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.0466427647
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "もしそうなら嬉しいです。これからもみんなと\n刺激を与え合って成長していきたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "もしそうなら嬉しいです。これからもみんなと\n刺激を与え合って成長していきたいです",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0466427647,
      "endTime": 102.06491926540001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……。ところで、さっきから隠れて\n愛を見守っている子がいるな。頭の角が見えているぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そうだな……。ところで、さっきから隠れて\n愛を見守っている子がいるな。頭の角が見えているぞ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.271585894,
      "endTime": 111.1009733681,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9036.054293399999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.1000001113
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.3076401874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……気付かれちゃいましたか……\nでも、隠れて愛ちゃんを見守ってた訳じゃないですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "えへへ……気付かれちゃいましたか……\nでも、隠れて愛ちゃんを見守ってた訳じゃないですよ？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3076401874,
      "endTime": 119.8576401874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.0709735398
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "たまたま通りかかって、たまたま立ち聞きしちゃった\nだけですから。そこは勘違いしないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "たまたま通りかかって、たまたま立ち聞きしちゃった\nだけですから。そこは勘違いしないで下さい",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.0709735398,
      "endTime": 127.4796356682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.6863024875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "こころ……聞いてたんだ……。丁度良かった\nこころにもお礼を言っておきたかったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "こころ……聞いてたんだ……。丁度良かった\nこころにもお礼を言っておきたかったんだ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.6863024875,
      "endTime": 136.75900089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.9656675184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "こころが私をチームリーダーに推薦してくれたこと\n最初はなんでって思ったけど……今は感謝してるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "こころが私をチームリーダーに推薦してくれたこと\n最初はなんでって思ったけど……今は感謝してるんだよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.9656675184,
      "endTime": 146.101744255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_05-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "私は遠慮しがちだから、あれがなかったら\nここまで積極的にみんなと関わらなかったと思う……",
